1.9
log
@Document bwi(4) interrupt error flags by using named constants
instead of magic numbers. Constants found in Linux brcmsmac.
ok claudio@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: bwireg.h,v 1.8 2013/11/26 20:33:15 deraadt Exp $	*/

